  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK596">
<l>uḷḷuva tellā muyarvuḷḷal maṟṟatu </l>
<l> taḷḷiṉun taḷḷāmai nīrttu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In all that a king thinks of, let him think of his greatness; and if it should be thrust from him (by fate), it will have the nature of not being thrust from him.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>
